1. *Bogu* se moli da nas čuva i da nam pomogne. (We pray to God to keep us safe and to help us.)
2. *Bogu* se zahvaljujemo na svim dobrim stvarima u našim životima. (We thank God for all the good things in our lives.)
3. Svi smo stvoreni po *Bogu*. (We are all created in the image of God.)
4. Od srca *Bogu* zahvaljujem za sve. (I give thanks to God from the bottom of my heart for everything.)
5. Čuvanje *Bogu* date zapovesti je važno. (Keeping the commandments given by God is important.)